-----------------------------------
INSTALLATION:
-----------------------------------
1. Copy the contents of the "lcrc" file to "~/.lcrc"
2. Install the following:
   sudo apt-get python-pip
   sudo pip install dropbox
   sudo pip install google-api-python-client
   sudo pip install 'python-skydrive[standalone]'
   sudo pip install requests
   sudo pip install httplib2
   sudo apt-get install python-tk
3. Create a folder named 'easyCloud' in your home-directory and in each of your cloud accounts. This folder would contain the stuff you want to share.

To use the application:
1. Double-click gui.py in the "Application Code" folder.
   		       OR
1. run "python gui.py" in the "Application Code" folder.